header.gameNote: PAC-12 MEN'S TOURNAMENT PRES. BY NEW YORK LIFE - SEMIFINAL

videos.description: Arizona's Lauri Markkanen follows up the 3-pointer with a mid-range jumper in the close game against UCLA.
videos.headline: Markkanen nails back-to-back jumpers

videos.description: TJ Leaf finds Isaac Hamilton in transition for the and-1 layup as UCLA and Arizona go back and forth in the first half.
videos.headline: UCLA's Hamilton completes 3-point play

videos.description: UCLA's Lonzo Ball misses the rebound attempt and appears to suffer an injury as the ball makes contact with his hand, but he would return to the game.
videos.headline: Lonzo Ball appears to injure hand, would remain in game

videos.description: Rawle Alkins gets by the defender with the spin move and finishes the layup as Arizona tries to pull away from UCLA.
videos.headline: Arizona's Alkins spins to the bucket for layup

videos.description: Allonzo Trier makes the step-back 3-pointer as Arizona extends their lead over UCLA in the second half.
videos.headline: Arizona widens the gap with 3-pointer

videos.description: Chance Comanche collects the rebound and capitalizes on the second chance opportunity by throwing down the two-handed dunk for Arizona.
videos.headline: Arizona's Comanche finishes with the strong two-handed dunk

videos.description: Lonzo Ball makes the 3-pointer after drawing contact to set up the 4-point play, as UCLA tries to get back in it against Arizona.
videos.headline: Lonzo Ball converts 4-point play

videos.description: Arizona's Lauri Markkanen makes the stop on the defensive end, which leads to the fast-break dunk by Rawle Alkins.
videos.headline: Block leads to fast-break dunk for UCLA

videos.description: Lauri Markkanen makes the 3-pointer as Arizona begins to build up a big lead against UCLA.
videos.headline: Markkanen connects from distance

videos.description: Lauri Markkanen finishes strong with the dunk as Arizona continues to control the game against UCLA.
videos.headline: Markkanen's dominant night continues with dunk

videos.description: Arizona's Lauri Markkanen catches the lob on the inbound play and finishes the alley-oop.
videos.headline: Markkanen with the emphatic finish

videos.description: Lauri Markkanen leads No. 7 Arizona with 29 points while No. 3 UCLA's Lonzo Ball is held to eight points, as the Wildcats win 86-75 in the Pac-12 semifinal.
videos.headline: Arizona takes rubber match from UCLA, advances to Pac-12 final
